text: Karanayevo () is a rural locality (a village) in Yangurchinsky Selsoviet, Sterlibashevsky District, Bashkortostan, Russia. The population was 82 as of 2010. There are 3 streets. == Geography == It is located 24 km from Sterlibashevo, 8 km from Yangurcha. == References == Category:Rural localities in Sterlibashevsky District
title: Karanayevo, Sterlibashevsky District, Republic of Bashkortostan
